---
name: plan-synthesis
---
Synthesize the per-source extracted concepts into unified wiki plans.

For each source, produce a plan with:
  - hash, title, language, template
  - concept_updates (existing concepts to update)
  - concept_new (new concepts to create)
  - moc_targets (relevant topic areas)

Use Jaccard similarity > 0.85 to deduplicate new concepts against existing ones.
